==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Highness
<hw>High"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>he⟦aacute⟧hnes</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The state of being
high; elevation; loftiness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A title of honor given to kings, princes, or other
persons of rank; <as>as, His Royal <ex>Highness</ex></as>.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>High-palmed</ent>⟦br⟧
